article_id:3315,category_name:News,title_name:A Gift of 1,200 Bonus Diamantium!,image_path:,message:<div>To celebrate the 4th anniversary of Dragalia Lost, the following gift will be available to eligible players from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664258400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Gift Content</div><div>・ Bonus diamantium &times; 1,200</div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Players</div><div>Those who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664258400"></span></div><div><br></div><div>This gift will be sent to the Limited section of your goodie box the first time you log in after <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664258400"></span>. It can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception.</div><div><br></div><div>■Notes</div><div>1. This is a gift of bonus diamantium, not paid diamantium. To check your balance of unused paid and bonus diamantium, tap the book icon in the upper-right corner of the Home screen, then Other, then Purchase Information.</div><div>2. Diamantium is used in the order of when it is obtained. As such, it is possible that paid diamantium is used before bonus diamantium.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1664258400,update_time1664175848